message: Skratka, zanimajo me cover komadi z ženskim vokalom (ki so bili v originalu odpeti z moškim vokalom), po možnosti bolj poznanih komadov, ki jih seveda odšpilajo in odpojejo bolj poznane pevke, ne stuff, ki ga folk na veliko snema na Youtubu...  Primer (Lacuna Coil - Losing My Religion):   Googlanje mi najde only as much, predvsem hoče prikazat doma posnete coverje kar me ne zanima najbolj...
je 1. jan 1970 ob 01:00 izjavil:bolj poznanih komadov, ki jih seveda odšpilajo in odpojejo bolj poznane pevke
Pevke niso najbolj znane, sicer. Po teh kriterijih imam shranjenih samo nekaj komadov:

Nina Hagen, Sunday Morning (The Velvet Underground, Lou Reed)    Nina Hagen, Hit me with your rythem stick (Ian Durry and the Bollocks)    Nina Hagen, Persona Jesus (Depechee Mode)    Nina Hagen, Hermann's Door (Bob Dylan)    Nina Hagen, I'm a believer (The Monkees)    Siouxsie and the Banshees - You're lost little girl 8The Doors)    Siouxsie and the Banshees - Passenger (Iggy Pop)    All About Eve - Last Christmas (Wham)

Nina Persson (The Cardigans, A Camp) je zapela kar nekaj zanimivih coverjev.  The Cardigans - Iron Man (Black Sabbath)   The Cardigans - Iron Man (First Try) (Black Sabbath)   The Cardigans - Sabbath Bloody Sabbath (Black Sabbath)   The Cardigans - Changes (Black Sabbath)   The Cardigans - Mr. Crowley (Black Sabbath)   The Cardigans - The Boys Are Back in Town (Thin Lizzy)   A Camp - Walking the Cow (Daniel Jonhston)   A Camp - Rock'n'Roll Ghost (The Replacements)   A Camp - The Bluest Eyes in Texas (Restless Heart)   A Camp - Boys Keep Swinging (David Bowie)   A Camp - Us and Them (Pink Floyd)   A Camp - I've Done It Again (Grace Jones)   The Cardigans & Tom Jones - Burning Down the House (Talking Heads)

Joan Baez sings Dylan. Bolj znano (pevka, komad) ne gre. Love Minus Zero/No LimitIt's All Over Now, Baby BlueYou Ain't Goin' NowhereIt Ain'T Me BabeI Pity The Poor ImmigrantTears Of RageLove Is Just a Four-Letter WordI Dreamed I Saw St.AugustFarewell, AngelinaDear LandlordOne Too Many MorningsI Shall Be Released (Extended version)Boots Of Spanish LeatherDaddy, You Been On My MindRestless FarewellDon't Think Twice, It's All RightWalls Of Red WingDrifter's EscapeWalkin' Down The LineNorth Country Blues
Hasta Siempre, Commandante (Carlos Puebla)    ... (zadnja niti ni tako znana pevka, je pa po pomoti pogosto naveedena Joan Baez)
Mislim, da je to najbolj znan cover z ženskim vokalom.   Tudi ta je zelo znan.   Če smo že pri njej.   Joan Jett.   Ajde naj bo.   Počasen Basket Case.   Pa še malo jazza za konec.
Tisti vprašajčki so interpretacija Unicode znakov, po naše Stenka Razin.  Helter Skelter - The Beatles

Drugače z "bolj znane" mislim tud stuff iz "moderne" pop/rock/metal scene. Ne vem, kakšen cover Linkin Parkov al pa mogoče Papa Roachov, kaj v tem smislu. Ker vidim, da limate kar precej očitno znanih komadov, ki mi niti niso kej dost poznani...
